As a tech leader, have you faced government funding for OSS stalling due to unclear ownership? The root cause is often missing legal entity details and compliant payment info.

Actionable steps:
1. Declare ownership (company/individual) and contact info in project READMEs;
2. Provide international payment details (SWIFT, tax ID);
3. Publicly endorse sustainable funding initiatives to build trust.

Sustainable open infrastructure requires collaboration—start with transparent payment information.
